comments: I did not expect to enjoy this hit but I actually did enjoy it. It was not easy but it was fun.
Study was enjoyable I wish there was a bonus or something to incentivize folks to try harder to get everything right.

I liked using a new word to describe things, and I liked the last quiz where it made me change the way I was typing the words the whole time. How to use heaned and milbed in a sentence when compared to small/big.
I enjoyed it and my little one enjoyed watching :)
It was better than similar hits of this type.
